title: Refrigerator Toe Kick Plate - White
description: Refrigerator Toe Kick Plate - White PartSelect Number PS11756055 Manufacturer Part Number WPW10534161 This kickplate grille is attached to the bottom of the refrigerator.

installationInstructions.author: Janet from SOUTH ST PAUL, MN
installationInstructions.title: Clips on old toe kick plate were broken on one side. Would not stay on
installationInstructions.content: Took the new kick plate out of the box. Snapped it into position. I have had a repairman for this refrigerator before. I would rather repair an appliance than buy a new one. I'm very proud that I thought to get a replacement part myself instead of calling my friendly repairman again. Saved a few dollars.
